headline: Intuit to Announce Third-Quarter Fiscal Year 2025 Results on May 22
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., April 30, 2025--Intuit Inc. (Nasdaq: INTU), the global financial technology platform that makes TurboTax, Credit Karma, QuickBooks, and Mailchimp, will announce its third-quarter financial results for fiscal year 2025 on May 22, following the close of market. The company’s third-quarter ends on April 30.
